# CLUSTERING APP
### Using K-Means Algorithm
 *-- By Mayank T. (R Enthusiast)*

---

## Statistical Clustering App

* Dynamic *(aka Reactive)* Application for Statistical Clustering 
  + Clustering based on K-Means Algorithm 
  + Reactive Data Summarization with 5 - Point statistical summary
  + Reactive Data structure specification for quick Syntactic know-how 



* Download the Cluster Results for deeper Insights 

---

## User Interface

* Quick Data Load in popular .CSV Format
* Designed to Auto-Read Variable tags
* Reactive Input handling for Dynamic Output Response
* [Hosted]( http://mayankte.shinyapps.io/clustering_app) Online,for Ready-Use with Zero SetUp Time


---

## Output Details

* Data Structure & Summary; *Example*

```{r,x1,echo=FALSE}
var1 <- c(1.1,2.2,3.3)
var2 <- c(3.1,8.2,5.3)
var3 <- c(2.1,1.2,9.3)
data <- data.frame(var1,var2,var3)
str(data)
```


* Data Means; *Example*

```{r,x2,echo=FALSE}
mean(data$var1)
```



* Clustering Outputs; *Explore More Yourself*
  + Cluster Size
  + Cluster Centres
  + Clustering Visualization


